        Parameters:
        aActor - A object examined by the resource manager to determine and track changes to resources. Each concrete implementation determines what is required to be passed. The Base implementation allows any object to be the actor.
        Returns:
        An Tx instance or null when the Tx cannot be created, such as the connection to the resource manager isn't available.
